{"word":"Τριτωνίς","slug":"Τριτωνίς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n105360\" key=\"*tritwni/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Τρῑτων-ίς</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ίδος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <sense id=\"n105360.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">Tritonis,</tr_> a lake in Libya famous in old Greek legends, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:20\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ P.\">P.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.20</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:178\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.178</biblScope> </bibl>; cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Τριτογένεια.</foreign> </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n105360.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> a spring in Arcadia, also connected by legends with the birth of Athena, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0525.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:26:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Paus.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.26.6</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n105360.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> a name of Athena (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Τριτογένεια</foreign>), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:109\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.109</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n105360.3\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> vase in the form of a Triton, <bibl n=\"http://www.trismegistos.org/text/78720\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PPetr.\">PPetr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2p.54</biblScope></bibl>, prob. in <bibl n=\"http://www.trismegistos.org/text/78721\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3p.113</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(iii B. C.)</date>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}